text: Astrée may refer to: * L'Astrée, a novel by Honoré d'Urfé or its main character * Astrée run-time error analyzer, a tool for static program analysis * Astrée (record label), a record label founded by Michel Bernstein * Astrée (Collasse), an opera by Pascal Collasse * Astrée (Typeface), a Deberny & Peignot typeface * French ship Astrée, a number of ships of the French Navy ==See also== *Astraea (disambiguation) *Astrea (disambiguation)
title: Astrée
